      alt="appt-logo"></a></h1>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="./appointment"><span id="create-appointment"></span>Create Appointment</a></li>
      <li><a href="/appointment/view-appointment"><span id="view-appointment"></span>View Appointments</a></li>
